summary: NAR 03/13/2003  THE CONSUMER HAS REQUESTED THAT THE VEHICLE GO UNDER EVALUATION  BY FORD TO DETECT PROBLEMS ON THE VEHICLE THAT WAS  NOT IDENTIFIED AFTER GOING ON THE DIAGNOSTIC MACHINE, BECAUSE THE CERTIFIED INSPECTOR IDENTIFIED RAW GAS IN THE TAIL PIPE  AND THE  SMELL WAS BECOMING INTOLERANT. THE CONSUMER WANTS  FURTHER INVESTIGATING .    *CB *JB
